		"name": "Express Interest - Complete API Collection",
		"description": "Comprehensive API collection for testing the redesigned Express Interest module with enterprise-level features.\n\n## Features Covered:\n- Send Interest\n- View Sent/Received Interests\n- Accept/Decline/Withdraw Interests\n- Personal Statistics\n- Compatibility Checking\n- Suggested Matches\n- Admin Operations\n- Analytics and Reporting\n\n## Authentication:\nAll endpoints require Bearer token authentication.\n\n## Test Data:\n- User IDs: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5\n- Test interests with various statuses\n- Compatibility scores and matching\n\n## Environment Variables:\n- {{base_url}}: API base URL (e.g., http://localhost:8080)\n- {{auth_token}}: JWT authentication token\n- {{user_id}}: Current user ID\n- {{target_user_id}}: Target user for interests",
